==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Thornbill
<hw>Thorn"bill`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any one of several species of small, brilliantly colored American
birds of the genus <gen>Rhamphomicron</gen>. They have a long, slender,
sharp bill, and feed upon honey, insects, and the juice of the sugar
cane.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

